description: Back home after their jungle adventures, Steve Hammond pays Jeff Stryker a visit and the two adversaries finally make nice. Steve lets his guard down and confesses his long-hidden affection for Jeff. The two men suddenly feel free to surrender to their passions and find happiness in each other's manly arms, celebrating everything thrilling and wonderful about man-on-man love.
title: Falcon Bareback - Fuck Me Raw #02, Scene #06
